FORMER Kaizer Chiefs and Bafana Bafana veteran defender Tsepo Masilela has has signed for AmaZulu.Masilela spend some time training with the club before putting pen on the paper on Friday. Masilela, 34, has been without a club since he parted ways with Chiefs at the end of the 2017/18 season. The club announced the signing of the experienced defender with a tweet which stated: "We are proud to announce that Tsepo Masilela has officially signed with AmaZulu for the rest of the season! ??Join us in welcoming the veteran defender ????#Usuthu_Pride'   